column5: Texas cottage in great location: Approx. 8 miles to the Domain and Whole Foods in Austin, TX. / 25 minutes to downtown Austin. / 4 miles to Dell Corporation in Round Rock and within 5 miles of The Dell Diamond and the Round Rock Express / Easy access to major roads and a Beeline to the airport. Entire home available. It is 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. Clean, light and airy, comfortable home with hospitable hosts.
